Im hoping GOD could read this and tell me what to do.  its kinda hard to forget a part, i've thought my whole life through.  its not that complicated, i've let others down too.  its not like you demand it, but im trying just for you.  Please try to understand me, and focus when you do.....I'll make it brief and to the point and maybe right on Cue.

I don't how i got this way or if i'll ever be ok......I hope to GOD we figure this before i'm really threw.  When you left, i guess i kept, alot of me with you.  i really knew i loved, my heart ached everyday.  i thought i'd never see you but wished it anyway.  The pain was overwhelming almost hard to bare.  Things piled up and life got rough, and things just seemed unfair.  I blamed myself for everything, it was the easiest thing to do.

Then drugs were then presented and soon i didn't care.  my life once had incentive and now it wasn't there.  i slowly went into depression, and wanted noone near.  I thought, "The drugs and me are all i need, to make it disappear.  People painted pictures in your head and made it seem that i was "dead."  The drugs, the Hate, The Violent state, was all that i could do.  I felt as though my life was gone the day that i lost you.  I knew i'd always Love you since the day i told you so, i tried so hard to hug you, and never let you go.  You see these weren't my real plans, and to be honest i'm not fine.  I'd take love over all the drugs, just to go back in time.  to that one day i woke to find, your pretty face asleep with mine.  

But here's some understanding for those who thought they knew, My life is only standing because i choose it too.  I'm trying now to fix things and hope its not too late, but know that i still love you and i hope its not too late........
